INSERT INTO `steps` VALUES (97,'Inclusive Communication','inclusive-communication','Support your learning about inclusive communication with these resources.','',0,'2020-12-15 22:53:12',1,'2021-02-21 22:46:37',1);
INSERT INTO `steps` VALUES (99,'Consider the Risks','consider-the-risks','<p>One of the Project Managers tasks at the Planning stage is to identify, qualify, and quantify the risks as they apply to your project. Knowing your risks and how likely they are to happen helps you plan what you will do in the event something comes along that impacts your project - sometimes this is a negative impact, but this could also present an opportnity! Knowing what the project will do to respond in any case creates a strong plan. </p><p>Risk assessment is done at the beginning, and revisited and updated throughout the project. The tools in this collection can help you with the tasks for risk assessment and mitigation.</p>','',0,'2021-01-22 18:58:47',1,'2021-02-21 22:46:37',1);
INSERT INTO `steps` VALUES (100,'Define the Quality ','define-the-quality','<p>Quality is the degree to which a set of inherent characteristics fulfills requirements.\" Establishing project quality standards involves determining which standards to use, and documenting how the project (and product) will demonstrate compliance. These standards provide a kind of umbrella for continuous improvement.</p><p>The resources in this collection are meant to support both the planning of quality standards and the whole teams efforts to work towards the projects quality targets throughout the lifecycle of a project.</p>','',0,'2021-01-22 19:06:51',1,'2021-02-21 22:46:37',1);
INSERT INTO `steps` VALUES (101,'Breaking Down the Work','breaking-down-the-work','<p>How do we break down project work to the most reasonable size task(s)? The point is to get a view of the work that allows tasks to be assigned to the responsible party, and allow the project manager to track progress during execution. </p><p>Resources in this collection support the team in creating a work breakdown structure and otherwise plan for the work completion in a specified timeframe.</p>','',0,'2021-01-22 19:11:03',1,'2021-02-21 22:46:37',1);
INSERT INTO `steps` VALUES (102,'Session 1: Welcome','session-1-welcome','<p>The pre-work has been designed to orient you to SBCPS and the supervisors role and responsibilities within the BC Public Service. Please complete the pre-work as listed below to be fully prepared for your first LIVE session on February 4th!</p><p>Remember to click on \"claim\" at the top left of each required pre-work item AFTER you have completed the activity.<br></p><p>For FAQs and information on how to use the Learning Curator, visit the top navigation on this page.</p><p>  </p>','',0,'2021-01-26 23:37:17',1,'2021-02-21 22:46:37',1);
INSERT INTO `steps` VALUES (103,'Session 2: Modelling Behaviour','session-2-modelling-behaviour','<p>During this session we will explore modelling behaviour in these contexts: <b>why</b>, <b>how</b>, and <b>what</b>. </p><p><b>Why </b>do supervisor responsibilities include modelling behaviour? <b>How</b> does modelling behavior consistently with humility and integrity, along with demonstrating cascading leadership direction support good practice? And <b>what</b> results can your expect as you carry out the mandates of supervisors in the BC Public Service?<br></p><p>Remember to click on \"claim\" at the top left of each required pre-work item AFTER you have completed the activity. For FAQs and information on how to use the Learning Curator, visit the top navigation on this page.<br></p>','',0,'2021-02-02 23:25:49',1,'2021-02-21 22:46:37',1);
INSERT INTO `steps` VALUES (105,'Session 3: Diverse and Inclusive Workplace','session-3-diverse-and-inclusive-workplace','<p>\"A lot of different flowers make a bouquet\". - Islamic Proverb</p><p>        Research has demonstrated that organizations and teams that value and encourage diversity, and more importantly inclusion, outperform, are more innovative and have higher employee engagement than those that do not.  This session assists supervisors in creating practical actions to promote D&amp;I within their teams.</p>','',0,'2021-02-11 17:17:52',1,'2021-02-21 22:46:37',1);
INSERT INTO `steps` VALUES (106,'Session 4: Collaborative Approach to Leading Virtual Teams','session-4-collaborative-approach-to-leading-virtual-teams','<p>In our previous two sessions, weve been exploring our role as supervisors and how we can contribute to creating inclusive workplaces through our behaviours and actions. </p><p><b> Collaborative leadership</b>, also referred to as democratic leadership, is an approach that aims to bring people out of silos to work together …particularly helpful as we navigate these times of change together with our teams. Whether you are a current or an aspiring supervisor, the \"Collaborative Approach to Leading Virtual Teams\" will be an opportunity for you to look at your current practices and consider behaviours and actions beneficial to incorporate into your supervisory practice. </p>','',0,'2021-02-12 23:52:24',1,'2021-02-21 22:46:37',1);
